{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_03_01_short",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 大人げない自分 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年が明けてから、数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Few days after new year",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "LizNoirは正月休みを返上し、特訓に励んでいた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir canceled their New Year's break and now working on special training.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……ダメよ、こんなんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa‚ haa… It's no good like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな！　今のところ、もう一回よ\n出来るまで、何度でもやるわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone! Let's do it again from the top.\nWe'll do it as many times as it takes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、ストップストップ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ stop‚ stop!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "貴方……いつから来てたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You… When did you arrive?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "もう一時間以上前からですよ\n新年の挨拶をしても気がついてくれなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been here for over an hour.\nI greeted you for the New Year‚ but you didn't notice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう……ごめんなさい\n……でも、今はレッスンを続けたいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… I'm sorry.\n…But right now‚ I want to continue the rehearsal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "話は後にしてちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's talk later‚ please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ダメです。こころも愛もバテてるじゃないですか\nそんな状態で続けても意味がない。休憩をとりましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's not possible. Kokoro and Ai are exhausted.\nIt's meaningless to continue in that state. Let's take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "……何言ってるの。知ってるでしょ？\n来週には今年最初のライブバトルがあるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What are you saying? You know‚ right?\nWe have the first live battle of the year next week.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}